item.description: C goes to the next open value because they collide resize is called if the table is >= being half full. The first 8 insertions before the resize: Put the existing keys (they rehash), then continue putting the rest of the list A is true B is false C is true (another case of A basically) D is false (another case of B) For get: best case runtime is O(1), worst case is O(n).
